node.text:
Time is ticking for every bear tortured by the senseless cruelty of the Bear Bile industry. There is no need for this abuse: there are cruelty-free synthetic and organic ingredients with the same medicinal properties as bear bile, so how can humans justify this abuse!? Luckily @world_animal_protection_uk are working to end the cycle of cruelty - it’s up to us to support them and empower them to tackle this head on. Link in bio ➡️ 

I made this comic with @paulgoodenough and @world_animal_protection_uk to raise awareness of this animal injustice 🐻❤️ Please give them all a follow, they’re doing amazing work. 

WHERE DOES YOUR MONEY GO
If you can afford it, please do consider donating. Every penny Rewriting Extinction raises goes directly to species-saving projects and restorying the planet with our 7 charity partners (Greenpeace, World Land Trust, Re:Wild, The Wildlife Trusts, Born Free, Reserva and Rewilding Europe).

node.text:
Many wanted to know what would happen next with Kathy.
"Soon" had kind of an open ending. Zeus will always know that Kathy was his whole family. That he was loved. 
A loving family is a privilege, but not everyone is so lucky. 
I hope it's not too distasteful to mention my book here again, but part of the proceeds will be donated to animal shelters and associations that help dogs like Zeus (before it's too late). We've already raised about $5000 for good causes now, I'm incredibly grateful for your donations and orders, Thank you so much!!! 
.
.
.
#webcomic #donation #lovingreaper #animalrights #dogsofinstagram #comic #BOOK #sadcomic #dogs #animalawareness
